description:
A simple list of more than 5000 words and associated meanings.

Useful for a quick review on the go.

updated quality of the content based on customer  feedback.


Covers words like:


A Series:Apostate, Apotheosis, Appease

D Series: Dainty, Dastard, Daunt

S Series: Sacrosanct, Sagacious, Salacious

F series:Fallacious, Facetious,Fatuous

I Series: Iconoclast, Idiosyncrasy, Idolatry, Idyll

M Series: Macabre, Macerate, Machination,

U Series: Ubiquitous, Ulterior, Umbrage, Uncouth
